data.description: This newly built 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom property in Winter Park is a must-see, offering modern living at its finest. The entire building was meticulously reconstructed from the ground up in 2021, exceeding the highest Florida Building Code requirements and standards, ensuring a safe and contemporary home. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a bright and airy interior with a fantastic split bedroom open floor plan. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring quartz countertops, a convenient breakfast bar, soft-close cabinetry, elegant gold finishes, and a brand new stainless steel Samsung appliance package, including a counter-depth refrigerator and a slide-in convection range. The master bedroom is a peaceful retreat, complete with LED-lit closets and a beautifully designed bathroom. The bathrooms throughout the home are nothing short of stunning, boasting floating vanities, LED illuminated and heated mirrors, euro-style one-piece water closets, frameless glass shower doors, gold finishes, floor-to-ceiling tile, oversized rainfall shower heads, and custom shower systems. The second and third bedrooms are thoughtfully tucked away off the hallway, providing privacy for guests. Each bedroom features multi-setting propeller-style ceiling fans, ample closet space, and striking matte black door hardware. Outdoor living is a joy, with a large front porch perfect for relaxing and taking in views of the lushly landscaped yard. This home seamlessly combines city living with a touch of nature, making it a truly unique opportunity. Location is key, and this home is ideally situated just blocks from the Dubsdread Golf Course and approximately 2 miles from Winter Park Village and the shops and restaurants of Park Avenue. Notable features of this property include a new HVAC system with a heat pump (2021), fresh interior and exterior paint, updated plumbing, a new energy-efficient highly reflective roof, a complete electric system with new wiring, energy-efficient Low-e double pane windows, a skylight, and new exterior doors. The brand new septic system in 2023 ensures peace of mind, and the highest possible insulation in all exterior walls and ceiling space provides optimal energy efficiency. The privacy-fenced backyard is perfect for outdoor activities, and the property includes a finished privacy block wall, complete irrigation, and a comprehensive landscaping package. Waterproof laminate and porcelain tile flooring run throughout the entire home, offering both style and durability. With a new membrane roof and AC system, providing long-term assurance. Don't miss the opportunity to call this meticulously crafted, modern property in Winter Park your new home.
